#Neon Biker Theme

An 80s synthwave/retrowave theme for the WiFi Pineapple Pager featuring neon colors, grid landscapes, and a cyberpunk aesthetic.

## Preview

![Dashboard](assets/dashboard/wargames_bg.png)

## Features

- Hot pink and cyan neon color palette
- Synthwave grid backgrounds on all screens
- Custom neon-styled battery icons
- Retro boot animation with loading bar
- Cyberpunk aesthetic throughout UI

## Color Palette

| Color | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| Hot Pink | #FF1493 | Primary accent |
| Cyan | #00FFFF | Secondary accent |
| Purple | #9400D3 | Tertiary accent |
| Dark BG | #0A0A14 | Background |

## Installation

1. Copy theme folder to `/root/themes/neon-biker` on your Pager
2. Go to Settings → Display → Theme
3. Select `neon-biker`

